{
  "ep": "01",
  "title": "シロクマ　カフェー へようこそ",
  "scenes": [
    {
      "audio": 0,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "笹を食べながらのんびりするのは最高だなぁ",
          "en": "It's the best to relax while eating bamboo."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 1,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "ちょっと またこの子は昼間からゴロゴロして",
          "en": "Oh dear, this little one is lounging around again in the middle of the day."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 2,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "掃除の邪魔よ どきなさい",
          "en": "You're in the way of my cleaning. Move aside."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 3,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "はいー",
          "en": "Okayー"
        },
        {
          "ja": "お母さん おかわり",
          "en": "Mom, can I have seconds?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 4,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "どうするの あなた将来は",
          "en": "What are you going to do about your future?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 5,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "もう ゴロゴロしてるときに 将来の話なんかしないでよ",
          "en": "Don't talk about the future when I'm just trying to relax."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 6,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "暇があるなら ちょっとはバイトでも探しなさい",
          "en": "If you have free time, why don't you look for a part-time job?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 7,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "ええ ゴロゴロするのに忙しいから 後にするよ",
          "en": "Yeah, I'm too busy lazing around, so I'll do it later."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 8,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "ああー 吸わないで",
          "en": "Ahh, don't suck it up."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 9,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "もう",
          "en": "Enough already."
        },
        {
          "ja": "どうしてお母さんはゴロゴロする忙しさが分かんないんだろな",
          "en": "Why doesn't Mom understand how busy I am with just lounging around?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 10,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "えーと 働かないでお金がもらえる仕事が載っているのはどれですか",
          "en": "Um, which one of these lists jobs where you can get paid without working?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 11,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "ないと思います",
          "en": "I don't think there is one."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 12,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "え",
          "en": "Huh?"
        },
        {
          "ja": "どうせなら お洒落なバイトがいいなぁ",
          "en": "If I'm going to do it, I'd prefer a stylish part-time job."
        },
        {
          "ja": "あ これいいな",
          "en": "Oh, this looks good."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 13,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "はい",
          "en": "Yes"
        },
        {
          "ja": "あ もしもし パンダと申しますが",
          "en": "Ah, hello, this is Panda speaking."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 14,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "そちらでデザイナーのアルバイト募集してますよね",
          "en": "You're hiring for a designer part-time position, right?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 15,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "ええ そうですよ 経験は？",
          "en": "Yes, that's right. Do you have any experience?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 16,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "ありません",
          "en": "I don't have any."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 17,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "パソコンのマウスは使えますか",
          "en": "Can you use a computer mouse?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 18,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "使えないです あんまり細かい作業はできません",
          "en": "I can't use it. I can't really do detailed work."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 19,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "そうですか",
          "en": "I see."
        },
        {
          "ja": "得意なことはありますか",
          "en": "Is there anything you're good at?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 20,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "あります",
          "en": "Yes, there is."
        },
        {
          "ja": "笹を食べたり 寝ながらぼんやりするのが得意です",
          "en": "I'm good at eating bamboo and lounging around daydreaming."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 21,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "あれ もしもーし",
          "en": "Hello? Can you hear me?"
        },
        {
          "ja": "もしもし そちらでインテリアコーディネーターも募集してますよね",
          "en": "Hello, you're also hiring interior coordinators there, right?"
        },
        {
          "ja": "はい",
          "en": "Yes"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 22,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "インテリアコーディネーターって なんですか",
          "en": "What is an interior coordinator?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 23,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "またゴロゴロして",
          "en": "Lounging around again."
        },
        {
          "ja": "アルバイト見つかったの",
          "en": "Did you find a part-time job?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 24,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "全然ないよ",
          "en": "Not at all."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 25,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "確かコンビニで募集してたでしょう",
          "en": "They were definitely hiring at the convenience store, right?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 26,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "コンビニ",
          "en": "Convenience store."
        },
        {
          "ja": "品数多過ぎるよ 覚えられないよ",
          "en": "There are too many items. I can't remember them all."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 27,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "あー 吸わないで",
          "en": "Ah, don't smoke."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 28,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "もう 外でだらだらしようっと",
          "en": "I'm just going to hang out outside."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 29,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "ははは あら 糸屑",
          "en": "Haha, oh, a piece of lint."
        },
        {
          "ja": "あ 取って",
          "en": "Oh, let me get that."
        },
        {
          "ja": "うん 取れた",
          "en": "Yeah, got it."
        },
        {
          "ja": "ありがとう",
          "en": "Thank you."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 30,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "じっとしてて",
          "en": "Hold still."
        },
        {
          "ja": "あ 待って",
          "en": "Oh, wait."
