    },
    {
      "audio": 47,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "うん 人手が足りなくて",
          "en": "Yeah, they're short-staffed."
        },
        {
          "ja": "ペンギンさん どう",
          "en": "How about you, Penguin?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 48,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "え？僕お客とバイトの両立 できるかな",
          "en": "Huh? Do you think I can manage being both a customer and a part-timer?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 49,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "ウーソ これから四名ほど 面接に来るんだよ",
          "en": "No way, about four people are coming for interviews soon."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 50,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "なんだ ちょっと考えちゃったよ",
          "en": "Oh, I was just thinking about it for a moment."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 51,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "僕もいいですか",
          "en": "Can I join too?"
        },
        {
          "ja": "僕もアルバイトしたいと思って",
          "en": "I was thinking I'd like to get a part-time job too."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 52,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "受けてみる 面接",
          "en": "Try the interview."
        },
        {
          "ja": "あ",
          "en": "Ah."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "audio": 53,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "では 最初の方 どうぞ",
          "en": "Well then, the first person, please go ahead."
